/wp.me\/p95VHY-2vQ","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":43304,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/22\/faith-not-coexist-avarice\/","url_meta":{"origin":9662,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Greed: Faith does not coexist with avarice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 22, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGreed and faith are never combined within the heart of a servant.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304\u2019i\u0304 3109 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u00a0\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062c\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0639\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064f\u0651\u062d\u064f\u0651 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0625\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646\u064f \u0641\u064a \u0642\u0644\u0628\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35811,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/27\/iman-shuhh-combined\/","url_meta":{"origin":9662,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Greed: Faith and miserliness never combined in heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe dust in the way of Allah and the smoke of Hell can never be combined on the face of a man. Greed and faith can never be combined in the heart.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 3111\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33178,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/11\/faith-jihad-hajj-best-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":9662,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Deeds: Faith, Jihad, Hajj better than all other deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019iz al-Tamimi reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \u201cWhich deeds are best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith in Allah alone, then jihad, and then a blessed pilgrimage are better than all other deeds like the distance between the rising of the sun and its setting.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24586,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/04\/02\/nothing-saves-like-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":9662,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Nothing saves you like remembrance of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 2, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe son of Adam never acts with a deed better to save him from the punishment of Allah than with the remembrance of Allah.\u201d It was said, \u201cNot even jihad in the way of Allah?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12638,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/05\/grey-hairs-in-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":9662,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Elders: Gray hairs in Islam are a blessing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn 'Abasah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has grown a gray hair in the way of Allah, it will be a light for him on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1635 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirimdhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0648 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32727,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/09\/martyrs-protected-pain-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":9662,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Shahid: Martyrs protected from pain of death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe martyr does not feel the pain of being killed except as one of you feels the pinch of an insect bite.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1668 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u